<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>{{Zend_Db_Adapter_Pdo_Sqlite}} does not load the {{Zend_Db}} class, on which it depends; e.g., {{Zend_Db::FETCH_ALL}}. This means that if a developer wishes to instantiate the adapter class directly, instead of using {{Zend_Db::factory()}}, then the developer must add an extra {{require_once 'Zend/Db.php';}}</p>

    </div>
</div>

